title: Girlboss, Gaslight, Lovebomb
description:
Have you or someone you know ever suffered from lovebombing? In this week's episode of Unfazed and Unbothered, Camo opens up about the latest in their love life, Tasia celebrates her newfound freedom, and the two talk about how they became friends, how success has complicated other friendships, and so much more!
Go to Babbel.com and use promo code UNFAZED,
Go to MicrodoseGummies.com and use code UNFAZED to get free shipping & 30% off your 1st order.
Go to ThePillClub.com/unfazed to get your first birth control care package and donate to help more women in need of affordable birth control.
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
If you like the show, telling a friend about it would be helpful! You can text, email, Tweet, or send this link to a friend: https://bit.ly/UnfazedandUnbotheredPodcast
